0.title: About This Project
0.content: This repository aims to gather theoretical proposals of qLDPC codes from the scientific literature. Each code is characterized by its parameters: . | n: total number of data qubits | k: number of logical qubits | d: code distance | n_a: number of ancilla qubits | .
